    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, utilizing its six individual throttle bodies to deliver a surgical throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement check. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the suspension geometry remains true and the engine's harmonic balance is superb. A perfect candidate for an enthusiast seeking pure analog performance.",
