    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 sports coupe that perfectly balances performance with daily usability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014typical of spirited highway driving\u2014are present upon close inspection. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium navigation system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a fresh brake fluid flush and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The engine pulls strongly, and the transmission shifts with crisp precision. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next enthusiast owner. Includes two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a thick folder of service receipts.",
