    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, the drivetrain is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis retains its communicative feedback with refreshed bushings and a balanced weight distribution. Cosmetically honest with minor patina consistent with its mileage, this is a turn-key performance machine ready for the canyons.",
